What is the DOM?
    A document object model is a representation of the data in a webpage but in object form
What is an event?
    An event is your interaction with the webpage as well as things that manipulate the page
What is an event listener?
    An event listener is a piece of code made to listen for events and execute another thing.
Why would we convert a NodeList into an Array?
    So that you can use all the array methods.
What is a component?
    A component is a function that is used to make one thing but with different
    content so that you don't have to rewrite code everytime you need to make another 
    of that thing. 